text: {| |} MV Magnum is a cargo ship in service with Magnum Shipping of Belize City, Belize. It was built in 1979 and initially in service with a Russian shipping company and was, until 2009, known as Znamya Oktyabra (meaning The White Banner). It is configured to carry wood or wood products, and is based in Phnom Penh, Cambodia. Its callsign is XUNA3. ==References== * Russian Maritime Register of Shipping Category:Merchant ships of Russia Category:Merchant ships of Cambodia Category:1979 ships
